  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of the effect of water and soap irrigation with Povidone-iodine And normal salin
      treatment of patients with ununion laparatomy or episiotomy wound ( a pilot study)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      IN Comparison of the effect of water and soap irrigation with Povidone-iodine And normal
      salin treatment of patients with ununion laparatomy or episiotomy wound ( a pilot study), We
      use soap in one group and Povidone-iodine And normal salin in other group for irrigation of
      ununion laparatomy or episiotomy wound.it`s require the patients in Povidone-iodine And
      normal salin group be at hospital till wound be able to closed.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
